			<div id="tabs-1">
			    <h2>开关</h2>
				     &nbsp&nbsp<input type="checkbox" name="time_open" id="time_open" value=1 onclick="time_control()">是否启用
				<div id="time_set_mini" >   
					<h2>您希望本策略在一天中的什么时间执行：</h2>
					<table>
					  <tr>
						<td align="right"><span class="fontRed">*</span> 开始时间1:</td>				
